data.description: This charming ranch home is nestled in the well established neighborhood of Quail Run. The front porch beckons you to sit a spell while enjoying your favorite beverage. When you walk inside, you are greeted with gleaming laminate floors, tall smooth ceilings and tons of natural light throughout the home. The living room is adorned with a cozy fireplace, setting the perfect atmosphere when hosting family and friends. The kitchen features stunning granite countertops and new appliances. The master bedroom is complete with an en-suite bathroom with walk-in shower. The finished attic room is the perfect bonus bedroom or office! Take a step outside and enjoy the large private backyard featuring a back deck, great for alfresco dining or grilling out, and a wired workshop. This home is conveniently located just a short 8 minute drive from downtown Rock Hill, where you will find an abundance of local shopping, dining and entertainment options! Don't wait! Come see this home today!
